# DataTables Server-side Processing Library for CodeIgniter

This library simplifies the use of the server-side feature of the DataTables jQuery library with CodeIgniter 3 and 4. It provides an easy-to-manage to integrate DataTables with your CodeIgniter applications.

## Features

- **Compatibility:** Works with both CodeIgniter 3 and CodeIgniter 4.
- **Easy Integration:** Simplifies the integration of DataTables server-side processing with your existing CodeIgniter projects.
- **Efficient Management:** Provides a straightforward approach to manage DataTables server-side requests and responses.


